Plasmatic fire manifests stronger when put in
direkt contact with sub-organic matter. The 
anti-resiliance of the material absorbs nuances
of combustion, causing eruption of node parts.
Divided in multiples, the protocol acquires its
own laws of movement, wave upon wave of below 0
and overheated parasytic relations. The snake
is a manifestation of its power, its presence
in the influx of desobediance of patterns. 
It sorrounds itself on its own predatory confinment, 
bringing forth all its individual necessities. 
It spreads its body on holes and flaws of the
matter, crawling and sliding invisible energy.
